* ============================================================
* INDEX V64 CDX/LMDB SMOKE v2
* ============================================================
* Purpose:
*   Test current v64 index rule:
*     v64 tables use CDX/LMDB for active order.
*
* Scope:
*   Non-destructive except disposable copy.
*   Uses SANDBOX.
*   Does not test INX/CNX active-order on v64.
*
* Key correction:
*   COPY TO requires the source table to remain open.
* ============================================================

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO INDEX V64 CDX/LMDB SMOKE v2
ECHO ============================================================

DO SANDBOX
WORKSPACE CLOSE

ECHO
ECHO --- OPEN ORIGINAL STUDENTS AND CONFIRM V64/CDX ---
USE students
AREA
FIELDS
COUNT
TOP
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA

ECHO
ECHO --- ATTACH CDX AND ORDER BY LNAME ---
SET INDEX TO students
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
AREA
TOP
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA
SMARTLIST LNAME,FNAME,SID NEXT 10

ECHO
ECHO --- SEEK / FIND / LOCATE UNDER CDX ORDER ---
SEEK WHITE
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA
FIND MARTIN
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA
LOCATE FOR LNAME = CLARK
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA

ECHO
ECHO --- SWITCH ORDER TO SID ---
SET ORDER TO TAG SID
AREA
TOP
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA
SEEK 50000016
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA

ECHO
ECHO --- MAKE DISPOSABLE COPY ---
USE students
COPY TO students_cdx_smoke WITH SIDECARS OVERWRITE
CLOSE
USE students_cdx_smoke
AREA
COUNT
TOP
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA

ECHO
ECHO --- BUILD/ATTACH CDX FOR DISPOSABLE COPY ---
BUILDLMDB AUTO
SET INDEX TO students_cdx_smoke
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
AREA
SMARTLIST LNAME,FNAME,SID NEXT 10

ECHO
ECHO --- MUTATE INDEXED FIELD AND VERIFY SEEK ---
TOP
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA
REPLACE LNAME WITH "ZZZ_CDX_SMOKE"
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA

ECHO
ECHO --- SEEK MUTATED VALUE ---
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
SEEK ZZZ_CDX_SMOKE
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA

ECHO
ECHO --- RESTORE MUTATED FIELD ---
REPLACE LNAME WITH "GRIMWOOD"
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA
SEEK GRIMWOOD
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA

ECHO
ECHO --- CLEAR ORDER / PHYSICAL CHECK ---
SET ORDER TO 0
AREA
TOP
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA
BOTTOM
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,DOB,MAJOR,GPA

ECHO
ECHO --- CLOSE; CLEANUP MAY NEED MANUAL FILE ERASE IF ERASE TABLE DOES NOT FIND COPY ---
CLOSE
ECHO Suggested manual cleanup if needed:
ECHO ERASE students_cdx_smoke.dbf and students_cdx_smoke.cdx / LMDB sidecars from SANDBOX paths.

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO INDEX V64 CDX/LMDB SMOKE v2 DONE
ECHO ============================================================
